NAME
    ok - Alternative to Test::More::use_ok

SYNOPSIS
        use ok 'Some::Module';

DESCRIPTION
    With this module, simply change all "use_ok" in test scripts to "use
    ok", and they will be executed at "BEGIN" time.

    Please see Test::use::ok for the full description.

